<mark><b>"METRONAKA"</b></mark><i>RedLine stop @ Sunset & Vermont</i>
<b>Duration:</b> 3 qtr (30 wks)
<b>Project:</b> Model Making, Architectural Drawings, Architectural Design, Business planning
<b>Programs:</b> Adobe Ai, Ps, Rhino 6

The premise of the studio focuses on how co-working today shapes the architectural technology involved with creating those particular spaces to accommodate a shifting industry of temporal office spaces in large cities.

